i am here today not merely to endorse a presidential contender but to make a statement of conscience, to stand as a matter of principle with one who has stood consistently for the needs of the many against the greed of the few,'' hightower said
jesse jackson is speaking in a clear and an articulate voice to an ignored majority of the american people whose lives have been frustrated, if not actually flattened, by the economic policies of recent years,'' the popular commissioner told a crowd of about 400 wednesday in the texas senate chamber
